Recently a woman filed for divorce in Mumbai after her husband complimented her look wearing a mask. Aman was always find  of complimenting his wife whenever she asked how she looked. READ ALSO: Alleged N19.6b LG missing fund: PDP faults lawmakers on Ihedioha’s probe But this time it was a trick question as mask covers most of the face and the wife wanted to know if Aman really means when he compliments her. When Aman said that ‘she looks good in the mask’, she understood that Aman doesn’t like her face. And that was it. All these years of complimenting went for a toss and Aman had to get divorced from his wife. Meanwhile there are many reasons for divorce to happen, but COVID-19 has brought some more new reasons.